British Foreign Minister compared the EU with the Soviet Union and prison
British Foreign Secretary Jeremy Hunt compared the European Union to the Soviet Union and accused Brussels of capturing the member states of the community.
This statement was made by the diplomat at the Congress of the ruling Conservative Party in Birmingham, which opened on Sunday, September 30.
According to the Daily Mail, thus Hunt commented on the difficulties in the Brexit negotiation process.
